puls-diskinfo (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * GTK4-based disk health monitoring application.
  * S.M.A.R.T. attribute display for ATA/SATA drives.
  * NVMe health information support.
  * Temperature monitoring with visual gauges.
  * Health status indicators (Good/Caution/Bad).
  * Support for HDD, SATA SSD, NVMe SSD, USB drives.
  * Polkit-based privilege escalation for SMART data reading.

 -- Puls DiskInfo Contributors <puls-diskinfo@users.noreply.github.com>  Wed, 11 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000
